  "title": "Laboratory Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Observe laboratory activities and accurately document results</li><li>Perform basic mathematical and laboratory calculations</li><li>Gather, organize, and prepare data for analysis and evaluation</li><li>Support laboratory operations by managing supplies and equipment</li><li>Set up, dismantle, clean, and store laboratory apparatus and glassware</li><li>Complete technical tasks and maintain records in compliance with company and regulatory standards</li><li>Ensure accuracy, quality, and data integrity in all documentation and procedures</li><li>Analyze chemical compounds and manage corporate compound inventories as required</li><li>Perform technical procedures across Production, Research & Development, Quality Control/Assurance, and Compliance/Environmental functions</li></ul><p></p>",
